item.description:
These are open to ALL paper crafters! Bring your projects, and get ready for a fun, productive night out. You will have access to my library of stamps, inks embossing folders and Big Shot dies and hundreds of card and scrapbook designs. You can even bring your dinner, snacks or drinks with you!

Don't have a current project?  I have card kits, scrapbook pages and great ideas for any occasion.  I have several new card kits available for upcoming holidays!!

Please drop me an email or call if you think you will be here. Special gift for bringing a friend that is new to me.

Kids welcome with Mom!
$5 plus cost of supplies used.

 

Signup for my weekly newsletter at www.stampwithmarilyn.com.  Left hand side of my website.

LIKE me on Facebook at Stamp with Marilyn

 

Happy Stampin' and Scrappin'!

 

Marilyn SanClemente

978-458-0729
